                        shutting a communication pathway off for a period of time or to effect removal of an infected
                        system (quarantine) etc. SECCON has developed a continuous circle of protect, detect, respond
                        that
                        has proven effective to our clients.</p>
                    <p class="paragraph-lg">The Nigeria private security industry contributes an estimated 0.7% to GDP,
